@startuml
title Сценарий 3: Прерывание аудита при сбое системы
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

participant "AuditController" as Controller
participant "ChiefInspector" as Inspector
participant "Auditor" as Auditor
participant "VerificationSystem" as System
participant "FinancialReport" as Report

Controller -> Inspector : ProcessAudit(report, auditor, system, ...)
activate Inspector

Inspector -> Auditor : SignForReport(report, ...)
activate Auditor

Auditor -> System : PerformScan(report)
activate System
note right of System : RequestCount > 100
System --[#red]> Auditor : throw InvalidOperationException("System Malfunction")
deactivate System

Auditor --[#red]> Inspector : exception
deactivate Auditor

Inspector --[#red]> Controller : exception
deactivate Inspector

Controller -> Controller : HandleException()
Controller -> Inspector : OffDuty()
note over Controller : Процесс прерван из-за технического сбоя
@enduml